   626→ * Uses Supabase Auth natively - stores session tokens for authentication
   627→ * Automatically logs in the user after successful signup
   628→ *
   629→ * ✅ MIGRATED TO SUPABASE AUTH: No longer uses Bubble for signup
   630→ * Creates user in Supabase Auth + public.user (account_host deprecated)
   631→ *
   632→ * @param {string} email - User email
   633→ * @param {string} password - User password
   634→ * @param {string} retype - Password confirmation
   635→ * @param {Object} additionalData - Optional additional signup data
   636→ * @param {string} additionalData.firstName - User's first name
